INSERT INTO `fp` VALUES (4,9,' Ranka Aquagreens Bangalore','Kengeri','Apartment','savefiles/banner_1329727858.jpg','ranka-aquagreens-bangalore.jpg','<p>2/3 BHK Apartment over &amp; Get Spectacular lake views Free!<br /><br />Aesthetically modelled 2/3 BHK apartments overlooking a scenic lake and a uniquely landscaped herbal garden for the nature lovers. Located in Kengeri township and spanning an area of 2 acres, Ranka aquagreens is a nature friendly residential building with 100 apartments on offer.<br /><br />Ranka Aquagreens offers its residents the perfect life by staying amidst lush greenery whilst still being just a stone&rsquo;ï»¿s throw away from the heart of all the city&rsquo;s hustle bustle.<br /><br /><br />Ranka Aquagreens - by DRA Projects<br />Ranka Group has been one of the pioneers in the residential real estate space of Bangalore. Having forayed into the construction business in the 1980s the group has changed the landscape of the city and its footprint is conspicuous in ever nook and corner of Bangalore. DRA Projects Pvt Ltd.(DRA) was later formed as an off shoot by one of the group&rsquo;ï»¿s founding members. DRA has also since grown leaps and bounds and has left an idelible mark in the real esate world by promoting South India&rsquo;ï»¿s largest integrated residential townships - L&amp;T South City with Larsen &amp; Tubro.<br /><br />DRA is credited with: <br />Building more than 10 million sqft of residential space and over 2 million sqft of commercial space. <br />Having strategic alliances with other industry majors <br />Having extensive network of industry partner all through the value chain <br />Maintaining sound and strong financials - Zero debt<br /><br /><br />Lifestyle Amenities<br />&bull; Swimming Pool &bull; Toddler Pool &bull; Gym &bull; Tennis Court &bull; Jogging Track &bull; Lakefront Landscaped Garden with Gazebos Party Hall &bull; Kids Play Area &bull; Automatic 10 Pax Elevators <br />&bull; 24X7 Security &bull; Intercom facility in each unit &bull; Piped cooking gas with gas bank in complex* &bull; Two Maids / Servants Toilets in Basement &bull; Well appointed Basement &amp; Ground Floor Lobbies &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<address class=\\\"\\\\&quot;center\\\\&quot;\\\"><strong>4, Ranka Chambers, </strong><br /><strong>31 Cunningham Road </strong><br /><strong>Bangalore-52.</strong><br /><br /><strong>Mobile </strong><br /><strong>9900029200</strong><br /><br /><br /><strong>Email</strong><br /><strong>marketing@draas.com</strong>&nbsp;</address></center>','17-2-2012'),(5,15,'The Empyrean','Whitefield','Villas','savefiles/banner_1329727794.jpg','image.jpg','<p>About Project <br /><br /> The Empyrean is Bengaluru&rsquo;s FIRST TRULY INTEGRATED SUBURBAN TOWNSHIP spread across 230 acres, surrounded by 212 acres of green reserve and water bodies. With a vision to recreate the Bangalore of Yore with romantic leafy streets and lots of green and open spaces; the Empyrean is designed to provide all the comforts with a blend of modern architecture and rustic living. Master Planning of The Empyrean has been done by Aedas, the world&rsquo;s second largest architectural firm. <br /><br /> The integrated township is planned as an idyllic, green, low-rise, pedestrian-friendly and community oriented neighbourhood, with over 100 acres of open and green spaces. <br /><br />&nbsp;The Empyrean has all modern amenities including primary school, nursery school and health centre. It is well connected to the city through NH-207. Located between Whitefield and Sarjapur, it&rsquo;s just a 30 mins drive to these places. The proposed Satellite Town Ring Road (STRR) will enhance the connectivity to Bangalore International Airport and major IT hubs such as Hoskote, Whitefield, Sarjapur and Electronic City.&nbsp;<br /><br /> The Empyrean is a place for the discerning few and for those aspiring for luxurious lifestyle with lots of open spaces in the midst of nature; far enough for you to enjoy the quite serene environment away from the humdrum of busy city life. As you leave Whitefield and approach its natural settings in the countryside, The Empyrean lends an absolute change to your sense of living in a bursting-at-its-seams metro to that of entering a unique heavenly abode - Your own Paradise!!<br /><br /><br />About us - FIRE Luxur Developers Pvt. Ltd. <br /><br /> FIRE Luxur Developer is a unique attempt at creating a real estate organization with high levels of integrity and professionalism. The organization draws its strength from a highly qualified and vastly experienced team of professionals bringing together the best practices of various industries, going beyond real estate. <br /><br /> FIRE Luxur is a joint a venture of FIRE (First Indian Real Estate) Capital Fund. It is the first India-centric Real Estate fund to be registered with SEBI. FIRE Capital Fund was founded in 2004 to address a unique investment opportunity created by the coalescing of favorable economic and demographic trends, the current composition of the Indian real estate market and the fragmented nature of India&rsquo;s real estate development industry.<br /><br /> FIRE Luxur intends to create world class housing solutions - based on best technology platform available, with customer delight being the centre of all its efforts.<br /><br /> FIRE Luxur brings to you The Empyrean, luxury residences, and a place that&rsquo;s more than a home. The villas at The Empyrean are a continuing source of luxury and beauty. Located at a distance of 17 kms from Whitefield, The Empyrean will bring infinite peace and joy to your senses. Come nestle in a haven of peace and luxury.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><address><strong>FIRE Luxur Developers Pvt. Ltd.<br />\\\'Regent Prime\\\', Unit No: 102<br />First Floor, Proprety Bearing No: 48<br />Whitefield Main Road, Bangalore-560066, INDIA</strong><br /><strong>Tel: </strong><br /><strong> +91 80 42860010/ 20/ 30</strong><br /><br /><strong>Email ID:</strong><br /><strong>myparadise@the-empyrean.in&nbsp;</strong></address><center></center></center>','17-2-2012'),(6,11,'Sowparnika Chandrakantha','Chandapura','Apartment','savefiles/banner_1329727684.jpg','Sowparnika-chandrakantha-300x190.jpg','<p>About the project Sowparnika Chandrakantha<br /><br />Chandrakantha is the 22 project from sowparnika projects &amp; Infrastructure pvt ltd. Chandrakantha is located in Chembanahalli village near Dommasandra in Sarjapur Road , it&rsquo;s a 140 unit apartment with 35 flats on each floor ,G+3. Elegant, spacious and refined homes for the discerning few, who love to dream, live and enjoy life like never before. The most affordable masterpiece on Sarjapur road is yours for the taking. Spread on a sprawling and serene acre, 140units of refined living spaces crafted to fulfill your need for space and comfort beckon. Well-planned with pathways and landscapes make living here a delight. Each and every unit is Vaastu compliant with adequate ventilation; fantastic facilities and most importantly strategically located at the most happening part of Bangalore.<br /><br /><br />Amenities<br />Swimming pool , Club house, Children&rsquo;s play area, 24 hrs power back-up, A/C, Gym, Park , Jogging track, Landscaped gardens on all floor, Sewage treatment plant &amp; solar water</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><address><strong>Contact Us</strong><br /><strong>52/1 CHEMBANAHALLI</strong><br /><strong>NEAR DOMMASANDRA</strong><br /><strong>ANEKAL TALUK</strong><br /><strong>SARJAPUR MAIN ROAD</strong><br /><strong>BANGALORE - 560125</strong><br /><br /><strong>Contact No.</strong><br /><strong>+91 8861000456</strong><br /><strong>+91 9663614113</strong><br /><strong>+91 9663614115&nbsp;</strong></address><center></center></center>','17-2-2012'),(7,3,'Sanguine Homes','Electronic City','Villas','savefiles/banner_1329727599.jpg','image-20.jpg','<p>ABOUT THE PROJECT<br /><br />SANGUINE HOMES NEAR ELECTRONIC CITY BENGALURU<br /><br /> The fast paced development, globalization and highly competitive work environment has left most of us in a state of tremendous stress, strain and fatigue. In the present scenario, is it not a big dream to wish for a home amidst serene surroundings, tranquil and pollution free environment of soothing greenery? After a day&rsquo;s of enormous hard work, if you desire to have the luxury of such a home to relax - we are glad to announce that we have a solution - &ldquo;Sanguine Homes&rdquo;.<br /><br />&ldquo;Sanguine homes&rdquo; is an exclusive gated community with a limited number of cozy independent villas. We are very proud to say that &ldquo;Sanguine Homes&rdquo; is situated amidst a dream like setting of rich, lush green surroundings and pollution free environment. Though unbelievable, it is within close proximity to the core city of Bangalore. It is located at just 4 kms from WIPRO in electronic city and less than 1 km from HCL (SEZ) in Jigani industrial area. We, as a team of professional civil engineers, assure you of immaculate planning - all according to vasthu and thorough professional excellence in execution to produce a villa of best quality. Further more,Sanguine Home&nbsp;is supported by the luxury of fully loaded amenities with cent percent functional utility to the limit of one&rsquo;s imagination. All this is being offered at quite a reasonable price. To say in one line, it would be certainly be the best bet and worth its value to buy a villa at Sanguine Homes considering the location and the quality of the product.<br /><br /> It needs a little effort from your side to believe all this - have a glance at the few of our photographs pertaining to our earlier venture posted herein and take out some time visit our project site.<br /><br /><br />HIGHLIGHTS<br /><br /> - Exclusive Gated Community<br /> - Cozy Duplex Villas<br /> - Rich &amp; Lush Green Surroundings<br /> - Pure &amp; Pollution Free Environment<br /> - Value for Money (100%)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><address><strong>Contact Us</strong><br /><br /><strong>Mr. Mohan Babu</strong><br /><strong> +91 99866 98033</strong><br /><strong>E-mail: mohan@vintcs.com</strong><br /><br /><strong>Office:</strong><br /><strong> 332, 1st Floor, 6th Main,</strong><br /><strong> 6th Sector HSR Layout,</strong><br /><strong> Bengaluru - 560 102</strong><br /><strong>Url: www.vintcs.com</strong><br /><strong>E-mail: info@vintcs.com&nbsp;</strong></address><center></center></center>','17-2-2012'),(8,14,'Brindavan Gardens','Anekal','Villas','savefiles/banner_1329727507.jpg','srr-daisy-villa.jpg','<p>About Project<br /><br />Brindavan Gardens is a BMRDA-approved residential layout (LAO/92/2008-09), spread over 26 acres in First Phase and future plans (total 90 acres). Our community is conveniently located and accessible to the most vital areas of Bangalore City, including Electronic City, BIOCON, Bannergatta Road, Sarajpura, SIPCOT industrial area of hosur town and the proposed SEZ of hours. Also centrally located for easy transportation to major educational institutions, such as Sarala Birla Academy, Alliance Academy, Shridhi Sai Engineering College, etc. Within walkable distance to Anekal Railway Station, to which METRO rail service is proposed.</p>\r\n<p>Amenities<br /><br />&bull; All roads with street lights &amp; Asphalted roads. <br />&bull; More thane 45% of free for Roads, Parks and Civic amenities. <br />&bull; Underground water supply and sewage line connected to each plot. <br />&bull; 24 hour security arrangement for the entire layout. <br />&bull; Electricity connection. <br />&bull; All round compound wall built for the entire layout. <br />&bull; Waste water harvesting system <br />&bull; Club house with modern facility and health care equipments <br />&bull; Swimming pool and jogging track <br />&bull; Exclusive childrens park and play area<br /><br /><br /><br />Customer Pleasing Features<br /><br />&bull; On 300 Ft (Existing state High way) <br />&bull; Walk able distance to anekal railway station. <br />&bull; Close to alliance academy &amp; Shrdi sai Engineering College. <br />&bull; 10 Minutes drive from Srarala Birla Academy. <br />&bull; 12 Minutes drive from Electronic city &amp; Elevated Express Higway (Fly Over) <br />&bull; Very Frequent train services from Banglore city,Anekal-Devenahalli(Via Yeshavanthpura) and Hour. <br />&bull; Metro train services expected very soon at Anekal railway station. <br />&bull; Villa plots ready for construction.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><address><strong>Contact Us</strong><br /><br /><strong>SRR Homes. </strong><br /><strong>498/C, 15th Main, </strong><br /><strong>15th Cross, 4th Sector, </strong><br /><strong>HSR Layout </strong><br /><strong>Bangalore -560102, India</strong><br /><br /><strong>Email: sales@SrrHomes.in </strong><br /><br /><strong>Brindavan Gardens / Exurbia: </strong><br /><strong>Kavitha : 9008600435 </strong><br /><strong>Sanjeer : 9008600431&nbsp;</strong></address><center></center></center>','17-2-2012'),(9,10,'Century Linea','Jakkur','Apartment','savefiles/banner_1329727426.jpg','elev-image.jpg','<p>PROJECT DETAILS</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br /> A luxurious, aesthetic and environment-friendly home planned with a profound understanding of you. That is Century Linea in Jakkur. The thoughtful design ensures excellent cross ventilation and naturally well-lit interiors. The clean and serene environs refresh life. The easy access to prominent points and utilities in the city make life easy. The wide ranging and world class amenities spell pride.<br /> The attention to detail is remarkable. Simply put, Century Linea is everything you wished for. And more.</p>\r\n<p><br />FACILITIES &amp; AMENITIES</p>\r\n<p><br />Facilities &amp; Amenities | Clubhouse | Multi-purpose hall | Health club | Stroll way Swimming pool | Water supply | Stand-by-power | 24x7 security</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><address><strong>&nbsp;</strong></address><center></center></center>','17-2-2012'),(10,13,'Bindu Promoters And Developers','Magadi Road','Apartment','no.jpg','elevation1.jpg','<p>Overview<br /><br />Bindu Promoters and Developers offers luxurious flats at BEL Layout, Magadi Main road, Bangalore. These 2 &amp; 3 BHK apartments provide high quality and modern lifestyle. All the apartments are vasthu compliant. Deluxe Duplex Units are designed &amp; styled as an independent houses incorporating the security feeling of an apartment.</p>\r\n<p>Type BHK Size Price</p>\r\n<p><br />Apartments 2 BHK 1067 sq. ft. Rs. 28,22,064<br />Apartments 2 BHK 1121 sq. ft. Rs. 30,25,509&nbsp;<br />Apartments 3 BHK 1422 sq. ft. Rs. 38,00,915&nbsp;<br />Apartments 3 BHK 1438 sq. ft. Rs. 38,41,776&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br /><br /><br /><br />Features:</p>\r\n<p><br />Gymnazium<br />Swimming Pool<br />BDA approved<br />Intercom facility<br />Water softing plant<br />Separate Visitor Parking<br />Power backup<br />Lift<br />Sweage treatment plant<br />Park<br />Reserved Parking<br />Security<br />100 % Vasthu compliant<br />Private Terrace / Garden<br />No common walls / 3d ventilation <br /><br />Location Advantages</p>\r\n<p><br />10 Kms. from Railway Station<br />1 Km from hospital<br />40 kms from the Airport<br />1 km from the School<br />1.5 km from NICE road<br />2 km from Ring road<br /><br />Specifications for Apartments</p>\r\n<p><br />Structure <br />Seismic Zone II Resistance R.C.C frame structure with anti-termite<br /> treatment for the entire plinth.<br />Walls: <br />External &amp; internal walls of compressed concrete solid blocks masonry with cement mortar<br />Plaster: <br />External walls cement plaster with sponge finish &amp; internal walls with lime rendering smooth finish<br />Lobby and staircase with kota-stone</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><address><strong>Bindu Promoters and Developers</strong><br /><strong>#30/4, 46th Cross, 4th Block, Rajajinagar,</strong><br /><strong>Bangalore-560010.</strong><br /><strong>Ph: 23101354/55 </strong><br /><strong>Mobile : Dixit Shah: 9886833766</strong><br /><strong>Nainesh Shah: 9980132970 </strong><br /><strong>Email : bindu_999@rediffmail.com&nbsp;</strong></address><center></center></center>','17-2-2012'),(11,2,'Grandeur','Hebbal','Apartment','savefiles/banner_1329727141.jpg','elevation2.jpg','<p>Grandeur offers 2 / 3 BHK residential apartments in Bangalore. It is truly a modern residential complex, with 60 flats conceived and constructed aesthetically, keeping your convenience in mind. Close to Hebbal road, it&rsquo;s just few minutes away from your work place.<br /><br />Grandeur is located close to Manyata Tech Park, Lumbini garden and other software companies.</p>\r\n<p>Amenities</p>\r\n<p><br />Large swimming pool<br />Amphitheater<br />Health club<br />Library room<br />Guest room<br />Childrens play area<br />24x7 security<br />Landscaped area<br />Exclusively designed seperate club house<br />Indoor games<br />Location Advantages<br />Over looking Manyata Tech Park<br /> Overlooking Rachenahalli Lake<br />Close to Outer Ring road<br /> Close to upcoming Metro station<br /> Close to major hospitals, schools, Banks etc.<br /> Connected to the International Airport.</p>\r\n<p><br />Specifications</p>\r\n<p><br />Structure <br />R.C.C frame earth quake resistance structure<br />Walls <br />6&rdquo; cement solid blocks for exterior wall and 4&rdquo; solid block for internal walls<br />Flooring <br />Vitrified tiles flooring for living, dining and kitchen<br />Ceramic tiled flooring for balconies<br />Doors <br />Main door with seasonable teak wood frame with teak wood shutters and internal doors sal wood frame flush shutters<br />Kitchen <br />Black granite kitchen platform with stainless steel sink 2 ft. height dadoing in ceramic tiles<br />Electrical Work <br />Copper wiring with Anchor / Havel&rsquo;s cables with Anchor rider switches<br />TV and telephone points in the living room and master bedroom&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><address><strong>Contact Us</strong><br /><br /><strong>ATZ Properties</strong><br /><strong> 12/1, Plain Street, </strong><br /><strong>&nbsp;Infantry Road Cross, Bangalore</strong></address><address><strong>9686031122&sbquo;9686011122&nbsp;</strong></address><center></center></center>','17-2-2012'),(12,16,'Shri Diya Vilola','Sarjapur Road','Apartment','savefiles/banner_1329723830.jpg','el4.jpg','<p>Set on the hottest location of Bangalore, Sarjapura Main Road. SHRI DIYA VIOLA is a 110 apartment complex spread over 2 acres of land. Having 5 blocks in its sprawiling complex, SHRI DIYA VIOLA consists of luxury 2, 3 @&amp; 4 BHK spacious apartment.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>SHRI DIYA VIOLA aims to amplify the living standards of its residents by providing international standard facilities, superior infrastructure and high quality which really remain unmatched its class.<br /><br /> Being located 10 kms after Wipro corporate office off Sarjapura Main Road. The project is close to IT Hub of South Bangalore, Malls, Hospitals, Recreational Venues and major international class Education Institutions like DPS, TISB, Greenwood High, Inventure Academy, Indus International School ect.<br /> Quality, luxury and value being the core propositions of the project, it&rsquo;s just more than a wonderful experiance being a VIOLA-ite!<br /> Also, because of the presence of various IT, ITES, Non-IT Companies, MNCs, SEZs in South Bangalore; your investment in SHRI DIYA VIOLA would ensure high appreciation in the future.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><address><strong>Contact Us</strong><br /><br /><strong>Shri Diya Projects Pvt. Ltd.</strong><br /><strong> #180, 1st Floor, 8th Main, </strong><br /><strong> 14th Cross, 6th Sector, H.S.R. Layout, </strong><br /><strong> Bangalore - 560102&nbsp;</strong></address><address><strong>M.: + 91 - 9900028966 / 68</strong><br /><br /><strong>Tel.: + 91 - 80 - 25729501</strong><b