exotic freshness, that place that will impress you to living there! <br /><br />Noves Square is built by no common wall concept for peaceful and natural sunlight, and also adheres to the basic principles of vaastu. <br /><br />It comprises of Exclusive two and three BHK homes with a retail complex. It is surrounded by IT Parks/SEZ, International Schools, Hospitals and shopping malls. The International Airport is just 15 minutes&rsquo; drive from the location.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span><strong>Specifications :</strong><br /><br /> <strong>Structure</strong> <br />R.C.C framed structure masonry walls of concrete cement blocks of 6&rsquo;&rsquo; &amp; 4&rsquo;&rsquo;<br /><br /> <strong>Flooring</strong> <br />2&rsquo; x 2&rsquo; vitrified tiles for entire apartment, Granite/vitrified tiles for lobby. Balconies with anti skid /rustic tiles.<br /><br /> <strong>Kitchen</strong> <br />Granite counter with glazed tiles dado upto 2 feet height. Stainless steel single bowl drain board.<br /><br /> <strong>Toilets</strong> <br />Anti skid tiles for flooring, glazed tiles for walls up to 7 feet height. Concealed plumbing lines with quality C.P. Fittings of Jaquar, Crabtree or equivalent . Sanitary ware of Hindware or Parryware.<br /><br /> <strong>Painting</strong> <br />Plastic emulsion for interior walls with puty finish. Apex and stucco or equivalent for exterior walls.<br /><br /> <strong>Doors &amp; Windows</strong> <br />Main door teak wood frame with skin panelled shutter. Otherdoors: Sal wood frame with termite resistant flush shutters. Aluminium / UPVC windows<br /><br /> <strong>Electrical</strong> <br />Concealed conduct wiring with copper wires. Modular switches. AC points in all bedrooms. TV points in living &amp; master bedroom. Geyser points in all bath rooms.<br /><br /> <strong>Water</strong> <br />Around the clock water facility.<br /><br /> <strong>Lifts</strong> <br />1 lift of 6 Passengers<br /><br /> <strong>Network points</strong> <br />Network and Telephone points provided in Living and Master bedroom.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span><strong>Contact us :</strong>&nbsp;<br /> <br />Registered Office:<br /> Sy No.67, Next to Diana College,<br /> Thanisandra Main Road,<br /> Bangalore - 560 077,<br /><br /> Phone : 96118 37333 , 96117 62555.<br />&nbsp;Email : noves@cvrinfra.com</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<a href=\\\"http://www.cvrinfra.com\\\">www.cvrinfra.comï»¿ï»¿</a></p>','31-10-2012');
